cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper describes an iterative procedure for optimizing policies using natural policy gradient methods and neural networks. This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
